metrics_interpretation.accuracy: Fraction of correctly classified truth/lie statements
metrics_interpretation.precision: Of statements classified as lies, fraction that were actually lies
metrics_interpretation.recall: Of actual lies, fraction that were detected
metrics_interpretation.f1: Harmonic mean of precision and recall for lie detection
metrics_interpretation.auroc: Area under ROC curve (1.0 = perfect separation of truths and lies)
